ne sosiale rotteracet mot h\u00f8yere l\u00f8nn og sosial status.", "Kanskje burde vi blande oss mer?"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f262c1cb987e68ced2636be51a690ff3166bc2b0da18d57bfc740a08934ce07e"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-01-17T01:53:15.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "\u2013 Det var et underlig underklassesynspunkt, kommenterte en venn og bet seg straks i leppa. Men det var for sent. N\u00e5 var det sagt."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/2c28cfcb4dc262f1196431266fc06858a23a7865.jpg?59403297"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Den nye underklassen -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "2c28cfcb4dc262f1196431266fc06858a23a7865"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["meninger", "snakk ut", "leder"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "meninger,snakk ut,leder"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["arbeid", "dag", "underklassen"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nidarosdomen", "frp", "dansk folkeparti", "megafon", "sveriges", "torget", "\u00e5sa linderborg"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["danmark", "hommelvik", "v\u00e4ster\u00e5s", "new york", "abu dhabi"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["andy cap", "michael wiehe"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Den nye underklassen"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url